OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest Hospice's
OL,4,Ccelebrates its 50th birthday
OL,6,FTo celebrate, St Joseph's hosted a 70s
OL,7,Fthemed party for volunteers, patients,
OL,8,Fand their families. Former members of
OL,9,Fstaff and guest speakers also attended.
OL,11,FOne regular visitor to the hospice is
OL,12,FJasmine Williams Her mother, Cathy,
OL,13,Fwas diagnosed with brain cancer and
OL,14,Fspent the last few weeks of her life
OL,15,Fat St Joseph's.
