OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest Hospice's
OL,4,Ccelebrates its 50th birthday
OL,6,FJasmine said: "It's an amazing place-
OL,7,F my mum in her final weeks of brain
OL,8,Fcancer chose to come here. It was
OL,9,Famazing, the level of care was
OL,10,Foutstanding. The staff just put the
OL,11,Ffamily and the patient first"
OL,13,FAfter her death, Cathy's family
OL,14,Fadopted a tree on the 12 acres of
OL,15,Fwoodland at St Joseph's. It now bears
OL,16,Fa plaque with her name, and a yellow
OL,17,Fflower - her favourite colour.
OL,19,FJasmine said: "We come here to
OL,20,Fremember her, and it's such a gorgeous
OL,21,Fplace."
