OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest Hospice's
OL,4,Ccelebrates its 50th birthday
OL,6,FStaff at the hospice are also using
OL,7,Fthe anniversary to speak about the
OL,8,Fimportance of their work, and the
OL,9,Fdamage a lack of funding and cuts can
OL,10,Fhave.
OL,12,FChief Executive Mike Parr said:
OL,13,F"Frankly it hasn't been easy because
OL,14,Fwe are a charity, we get around a
OL,15,Fthird of our funding from the NHS but
OL,16,Fthe bulk comes from the community,
OL,17,Ffrom fundraising and donations.
