OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest Hospice's
OL,4,Ccelebrates its 50th birthday
OL,6,F"People still do donate, and we must
OL,7,Fnot lose sight of that. It's very
OL,8,Fhumbling how people come up with new
OL,9,Fways to raise funds."
OL,11,FAfter her mother received such great
OL,12,Fcare, Jasmine has continued to
OL,13,Ffundraise for St Joseph's Hospice. On
OL,14,FSunday 17 March she ran the Liverpool
OL,15,Fhalf marathon, raising #2,400 in the
OL,16,Fprocess.
OL,18,FShe said: "I know it's a small amount
OL,19,Fcompared to all the funding they need,
OL,20,Fbut at least it's something."
